to it.

00:21.427 --> 00:22.760
Hey, brooke.
How you doing?

00:22.828 --> 00:26.096
Yeah, I'm just watching
a teamster paint my adolescence

00:26.164 --> 00:27.697
A fugly shade of brown.

00:27.765 --> 00:30.769
Oh. I guess there's a lot
of memories around here for you.

00:30.837 --> 00:32.387
You could say that.

00:32.455 --> 00:35.390
In high school,
this was lucas' bedroom.

00:36.688 --> 00:40.004
Mm. Now that
<i>that's</i> burned into my brain,

00:40.072 --> 00:43.273
How we, uh, doing on the
wardrobe choices for scene 23?

00:43.341 --> 00:44.848
The big love scene --

00:44.916 --> 00:47.837
Slinky off-the-shoulder,
tight-and-revealing.

00:47.905 --> 00:48.239
Nice.

00:48.239 --> 00:50.552
I knew hiring you as costume
designer was the right move.

00:51.440 --> 00:52.449
Thank you.

00:52.653 --> 00:55.224
Let me see them on her
before I make a decision.

00:55.292 --> 00:57.482
So...[sighs]

00:57.550 --> 00:59.338
Speaking
of high school memories,

00:59.406 --> 01:01.794
Haley and quinn organized
that fundraiser dance

01:01.871 --> 01:03.314
At tree hill high
tonight.

01:03.382 --> 01:04.900
And I just wanted
to tell you

01:04.968 --> 01:07.153
In case you were thinking
it'd be weird to go.

01:07.220 --> 01:09.472
Not that you would.
But if you did...

01:09.540 --> 01:11.090
It wouldn't.

01:11.157 --> 01:13.541
Uh, thanks, but, you
know, we shoot our
first scenes tomorrow,

01:13.608 --> 01:14.923
And I got a million things
to do.

01:14.990 --> 01:17.038
Besides, you know what a geek
I was in high school.

01:17.106 --> 01:18.446
You've seen
my yearbook photo.

01:18.514 --> 01:20.728
Yeah, that's burned
into <i>my</i> brain.

01:20.796 --> 01:21.976
Exactly.

01:22.044 --> 01:24.958
The day I graduated,
I swore I'd never go back.

01:25.031 --> 01:27.445
You have fun, though.
I'll see you tomorrow.

01:27.513 --> 01:30.665
See you tomorrow.

01:30.733 --> 01:34.156
* ooooh, ooh, ooh, ooh *

01:34.224 --> 01:35.863
