01:43.477 --> 01:46.793
Clay, I'm here
for my morning laps.

01:46.861 --> 01:52.291
I even shaved certain...
Areas to cut down on my time.

01:52.359 --> 01:53.930
And yours.

01:53.998 --> 01:57.517
Ugh.
Just go away already.

01:57.584 --> 01:59.360
Ugh. Don't tell me
you're in there

01:59.427 --> 02:02.474
With that
miserable slag again.

02:02.542 --> 02:04.384
* ...Forget about me *

02:04.451 --> 02:07.094
