02:13.591 --> 02:17.708
[ sighs heavily ]

02:17.775 --> 02:20.353
* don't you *

02:20.421 --> 02:24.302
* forget about me *

02:24.370 --> 02:26.443
* as you walk on by *

02:26.511 --> 02:28.986
Sorry.
I'm such a slag.

02:29.054 --> 02:32.768
* will you call my name? *

02:32.836 --> 02:37.553
* as you walk on by *

02:37.621 --> 02:39.728
* will you call my name? *

02:39.796 --> 02:41.065
Guys?

02:41.133 --> 02:43.409
It's a little early
to be surfing for porn.

02:43.477 --> 02:44.580
Don't ever say that.

02:44.647 --> 02:45.683
Don't even <i>think</i> it.

02:45.751 --> 02:48.427
We're not looking at porn...
Yet.

02:48.495 --> 02:50.968
We're changing
your life.

02:51.036 --> 02:53.344
"cantwaittofindadate.Com"

02:53.412 --> 02:54.748
