02:54.816 --> 02:56.285
Listen, the best way
to get over millie

02:56.355 --> 02:57.692
Is to get right back
on the horse --

02:57.760 --> 03:00.535
Preferably a hot, naked,
made-to-order horse.

03:00.603 --> 03:03.411
