is describe your perfect woman.

03:18.089 --> 03:19.994
Hey, man.

03:20.062 --> 03:21.097
[ sighs ]
morning.

03:21.165 --> 03:22.636
Morning?

03:22.704 --> 03:24.006
Where the hell are we?

03:24.074 --> 03:26.414
We left that charity event
in atlanta early

03:26.482 --> 03:28.587
So we could make it back
to tree hill by morning.

03:28.655 --> 03:30.626
Yeah. Uh, right after
you fell asleep last night,

03:30.694 --> 03:31.863
It started raining.

03:31.930 --> 03:33.502
Yeah?

03:33.569 --> 03:35.305
Really hard.
And?

03:35.373 --> 03:37.546
One might even call it
a deluge.

03:37.614 --> 03:38.683
Clay.

03:40.690 --> 03:42.025
I missed the highway exit

03:42.093 --> 03:45.436
And, uh, drove a few hours
in the wrong direction.

03:45.503 --> 03:47.006
But the good news is

03:47.073 --> 03:49.045
That we're only a couple hundred
miles outside of tree hill,

03:49.112 --> 03:50.450
And we're driving
a corvette.

03:50.517 --> 03:52.789
We'll be home faster
than you can say yao ming.

03:53.693 --> 03:55.162
[ engine turns over ]

03:56.668 --> 03:57.870
[ tires pop ]

03:57.938 --> 04:00.075
[ tires deflating ]

04:02.649 --> 04:04.251
