04:27.765 --> 04:29.866
Bacon, crispy.

04:29.934 --> 04:31.667
Eggs, scrambled.
Milk, chocolate.

04:31.735 --> 04:34.369
Hey!
[ snaps fingers ]

04:34.437 --> 04:35.803
