to your mother?

04:38.572 --> 04:39.772
Uh...

04:39.840 --> 04:42.974
Pancakes, blueberry?

04:48.212 --> 04:50.045
I can't believe it.

04:50.113 --> 04:52.747
They frickin'
forgot my birthday.

04:56.521 --> 04:58.169
Haley, listen, my phone is bad to die.

04:58.169 --> 05:00.171
Everything's fine -- we're just
having some car trouble,

05:00.239 --> 05:01.773
