but, haley...

05:04.978 --> 05:06.445
Happy birthday.

05:06.513 --> 05:07.713
Well...

05:07.781 --> 05:09.215
* the salvation army band
plays *

05:09.282 --> 05:10.983
According to gomer pyle,

05:11.051 --> 05:13.553
