something.

05:24.365 --> 05:25.866
I...

05:25.934 --> 05:27.668
Let me use your phone.
Sure.

05:29.504 --> 05:31.805
It's in the car.

05:31.873 --> 05:35.108
* pushing the town away *

05:35.175 --> 05:36.742
