05:38.244 --> 05:39.878
* ah hey ma ma ma *

05:39.946 --> 05:42.612
Hey, alex, I just got
the gold script revisions,

05:42.680 --> 05:44.347
But I don't see
any changes.

05:44.415 --> 05:45.747
