on holidays and stuff.

06:32.213 --> 06:33.280
I don't know.

06:33.348 --> 06:35.681
Maybe it's the birth
of a new day.

06:35.749 --> 06:37.250
Are you feeling all right?

06:37.317 --> 06:38.518
Yeah. [ sighs ]

06:38.586 --> 06:40.653
