[ giggles ]

07:42.807 --> 07:44.107
Yay.

07:48.278 --> 07:49.879
Yeesh.

07:49.947 --> 07:53.516
I'd like my margarita blended,
no salt.

07:53.583 --> 07:54.949
Ha ha.

07:55.017 --> 07:57.251
