08:38.650 --> 08:40.551
Okay, cool.
I'll pick you up at 7:00.

08:40.619 --> 08:43.986
Oh, and by the way, for
the whole magnet thing to work,

08:44.054 --> 08:46.123
I'm gonna need you
to salvage that train wreck.

08:46.190 --> 08:47.957
Yeah.

08:59.299 --> 09:01.133
Quinn?

09:01.200 --> 09:02.434
Quinny,
are you up there?

09:02.501 --> 09:04.935
